  "actionable_ascii_heavy_residuals": [],
  "accepted_ascii_heavy_residuals": [
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:0",
      "text": "欢迎来到 RenderMan Fundamentals，这是 Pixar flagship renderer 的官方 introductory training。",
      "ascii_letters": 62,
      "cjk_chars": 9
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:2",
      "text": "PxrSurface Basics（PxrSurface 基础课程入口）",
      "ascii_letters": 26,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:3",
      "text": "Overview（课程概览）",
      "ascii_letters": 8,
      "cjk_chars": 4
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:4",
      "text": "本课会从 fundamentals 层面介绍 RenderMan 随附的优秀 Uber shader：PxrSurface。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 13
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:5",
      "text": "Diffuse（Diffuse 漫反射课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 14,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:6",
      "text": "在本课中，我们会探索如何在 PxrSurface material 中正确使用 Diffuse lobe，以及何时需要 linearize 你的 ACEScg 或 sRGB texture maps。",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 26
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:7",
      "text": "Artistic Specular（Artistic Specular 艺术化高光课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:8",
      "text": "这是两节 PxrSurface Specular lobes 课程中的第一节。本课会指导你如何在 Artistic mode 中工作。",
      "ascii_letters": 35,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:9",
      "text": "Physical Specular（Physical Specular 物理高光课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 32,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:10",
      "text": "在第二节 PxrSurface Specular lobes 课程中，我们会了解 Physical mode，以及如何使用 scientific values 创建 realistic metals。",
      "ascii_letters": 66,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:11",
      "text": "Conductors & Dielectrics（导体与电介质材质基础）",
      "ascii_letters": 21,
      "cjk_chars": 10
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:12",
      "text": "理解 Conductive 和 Dielectric materials 之间的区别，是创建美观且 realistic shaders 的关键。本课会提供你入门所需的全部 fundamentals。",
      "ascii_letters": 57,
      "cjk_chars": 30
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:13",
      "text": "Iridescence（虹彩参数课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:16",
      "text": "学习如何为 fabrics 添加 realism，并了解如何使用 Fuzz 为 assets 添加 dust 和 fine powder。",
      "ascii_letters": 38,
      "cjk_chars": 18
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:18",
      "text": "在这节 Glass lesson 中，你将学习 Glass lobe 内的全部 fundamental parameters。",
      "ascii_letters": 41,
      "cjk_chars": 12
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:21",
      "text": "Subsurface Scattering（次表面散射课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 20,
      "cjk_chars": 7
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:22",
      "text": "本课会介绍 RenderMan 中的 Subsurface Scattering，以及 PxrSurface 随附的各种 SSS models。请务必跟随 project file 一起练习！",
      "ascii_letters": 59,
      "cjk_chars": 23
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:23",
      "text": "PxrSurface Layering（PxrSurface 分层课程入口）",
      "ascii_letters": 28,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:24",
      "text": "Material Layering（材质分层课程）",
      "ascii_letters": 16,
      "cjk_chars": 6
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:25",
      "text": "在本课中，学习如何使用 versatile PxrLayerSurface material system 创建 sophisticated layered materials 的基础。请务必下载",
      "ascii_letters": 67,
      "cjk_chars": 20
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:26",
      "text": "Midnight Rebel",
      "ascii_letters": 13,
      "cjk_chars": 0
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:27",
      "text": "Maya project 来跟随练习！",
      "ascii_letters": 11,
      "cjk_chars": 5
    },
    {
      "item_id": "e57e51ae1b:29",
      "text": "现在你已经掌握了 PxrSurface material 的基础，下一课我们会了解来自 Industrial Light & Magic 的 MaterialX Lama shading system。",
      "ascii_letters": 64,
      "cjk_chars": 22
    }
  ],
